/hpc2hdd/home/xhao390/py/urbanclip/data/: The image captures a panoramic view of a bustling street in Beijing, China. The perspective is from a high vantage point, providing a bird's eye view of the urban landscape. The street, teeming with cars and buses, cuts through the heart of the city, flanked by towering buildings on both sides. The buildings, predominantly white and gray, rise high into the overcast sky, their windows reflecting the muted light of the day. Amidst the concrete jungle, patches of greenery peek through, adding a touch of nature to the urban setting. The overall color palette of the image is dominated by shades of gray and green, painting a picture of a city where modernity and nature coexist.
